    "description": "<p>Make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success: </strong>You create a sphere of fog with up to a 4 Space radius, centered on a point within range.<br><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> Radius +1 Space.&nbsp;<br><strong>Failure: </strong>3 Space radius.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The sphere spreads around corners, and its area is <strong>Fully Concealed</strong>. Creatures within 1 Space of each other see each&nbsp;other normally. It lasts for the duration or until a wind of moderate or greater speed disperses it.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Mana Point Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Area of Effect: (1 MP)&nbsp;</strong>Increase the radius of the spell effect by 3 Spaces.</li>\n</ul>",
